    "name": "Brentwood",
    "steam_appid": 3070010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles and uncover the secrets of Brentwood in this mysterious point-and-click adventure. The unique powers you hold will lead to moral choices that directly influence the story, the fate of the town, and which of the multiple endings you unlock. Will you follow destiny or fight against it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/553ea8a666da5b332f92f68d4d391a59.avif?t=1758401389\" width=616 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village of Brentwood seems nice and peaceful, but beneath the surface, many dark secrets are hidden that no one wants to talk about. It looks like your grandpa’s mysterious death has something to do with it. As you explore, you’ll uncover these secrets and piece together the truth behind his passing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/9368756db30245e15756988ee02cf129.poster.avif?t=1758401389\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/9368756db30245e15756988ee02cf129.webm?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/9368756db30245e15756988ee02cf129.mp4?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/f54c4492ecec96a23eaf2af1e75659f6.avif?t=1758401389\" width=616 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through the narrative by solving different puzzles, unlocking new parts of the story and bringing you closer to the truth.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/60e65ea5d1a69238e6065306b6f57c54.poster.avif?t=1758401389\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/60e65ea5d1a69238e6065306b6f57c54.webm?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/60e65ea5d1a69238e6065306b6f57c54.mp4?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/f65e10a6512a0f56177722051e03f3f8.avif?t=1758401389\" width=616 height=69 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Brentwood, you’ll find that even in a peaceful rural place disconnected from social media and the outside world, some villagers are still struggling daily. You’ll have meaningful conversations with residents dealing with grief, self-doubt, and societal expectations. Each interaction will reveal more about their lives and the village’s hidden past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/eed3d28b433d469e3cef707a7e040421.poster.avif?t=1758401389\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/eed3d28b433d469e3cef707a7e040421.webm?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/eed3d28b433d469e3cef707a7e040421.mp4?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/80de303bedafe170e08499829d13e187.avif?t=1758401389\" width=616 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you journey through Brentwood, your unique powers will reveal the fate of the residents you meet. You won't know how your actions will influence their destiny or the village as a whole. It’s up to you to figure out the truth behind these futures and decide whether to guide them toward their fate or not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/b329efe979dc475a3c551e37df2ca12f.poster.avif?t=1758401389\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/b329efe979dc475a3c551e37df2ca12f.webm?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/b329efe979dc475a3c551e37df2ca12f.mp4?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/e6199f649b60d772cce735c72981fc13.avif?t=1758401389\" width=616 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you uncover the secrets of Brentwood, your choices will have meaningful moral consequences. Every decision you make, big or small, directly influences the story and the fate of the town and its residents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/cf0afb9b68183cc721496fe4a409e67d.poster.avif?t=1758401389\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/cf0afb9b68183cc721496fe4a409e67d.webm?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/cf0afb9b68183cc721496fe4a409e67d.mp4?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/ecb76d5a3803fafdb540eb08178fd133.avif?t=1758401389\" width=616 height=69 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple endings to the game, and it’s up to you how the story will end. Based on the dialogue options you choose and the more you learn about the villagers, you’ll be able to influence their futures. Will you help them overcome their struggles and achieve their best future, or will you use this information to lead them to their darkest fate?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/810e51e3f744bdf720cd3a20b346e903.poster.avif?t=1758401389\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/810e51e3f744bdf720cd3a20b346e903.webm?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/810e51e3f744bdf720cd3a20b346e903.mp4?t=1758401389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
